			<h1 itemprop="name headline  "
								>Washington DC shooting: Aaron Alexis named as navy yard gunman – as it happened</h1>
		
					<p itemprop="description" id="stand-first"
				 class="stand-first-alone"                        	        data-component="Article:standfirst_cta"			>• 13 deaths after Washington naval yard shootings<br />• DC police confirm one gunman dead at scene<br />• Of two further suspects, one is ruled out<br />• Officials say incident is fluid and ongoing<br />•<a href="http://www.theguardian.com/world/2013/sep/16/washington-navy-yard-mass-shooting"> Read our news story on the Washington shooting</a></p>
		
		
