    <div class="block-elements">
            
	<p>The <strong>US navy</strong> has issued an "order to account" for all navy uniformed personnel following the shootings this morning.</p>
<p>The order applies to "both active duty and selected reserve, assigned to commands in the DC metro area. The order also applies to family members, navy civilian employees, as well as, NAF and NEX personnel."</p>
