    <div class="block-elements">
            
	<p>Twitter user <strong><a href="https://twitter.com/gerritt">@Gerritt</a></strong> is among those who are on lockdown in the US navy yard. Earlier he tweeted a picture as employees evacuated, now he posts this from the navy yard food court where staff are waiting for the yard to be secured.</p>
<p>DC police chief <strong>Cathy Lanier</strong> said earlier that it could be two hours before the site is secured.</p>
    
