    <div class="block-elements">
            
	<p>Ray Mabus, the US secretary of the navy, has issued his first comments on the shooting. <a href="https://twitter.com/SECNAV">Mabus tweeted</a> just now saying he was "shocked and saddened" by the situation.</p>
    
